Nah. It's hot.

533
00:38:40,520 --> 00:38:42,240
You don't need to stay too long.

534
00:38:42,320 --> 00:38:43,680
No, I don't wanna go.

535
00:38:44,160 --> 00:38:47,760
But there's a lot of stuff there.
Desserts and all that.

536
00:38:47,840 --> 00:38:49,480
You can just go with me.

537
00:38:51,640 --> 00:38:55,040
No, but I thought
you were craving desserts?

538
00:38:55,960 --> 00:38:59,960
Bua loi, foi thong,
custard bread, and stuff like that.

539
00:39:00,560 --> 00:39:01,960
Doesn't that sound tempting?

540
00:39:12,160 --> 00:39:13,920
- Hey.
- What?

541
00:39:14,000 --> 00:39:16,200
You asked me how to confess, right?

542
00:39:16,280 --> 00:39:17,600
Yeah, what should I do?

543
00:39:17,680 --> 00:39:19,200
Gotta have each other's backs.

544
00:39:20,080 --> 00:39:23,120
I've got a plan
for your confession, buddy.

545
00:39:25,560 --> 00:39:27,000
Buddy.

546
00:39:28,000 --> 00:39:30,360
- Buddy…
- That's what friends are for.

547
00:39:52,720 --> 00:39:54,000
- There he is.
- Where?

548
00:39:54,080 --> 00:39:55,520
- Where is he?
- Let's go.

549
00:40:02,960 --> 00:40:04,120
Who are you looking for?

550
00:40:04,200 --> 00:40:07,080
The one I'm meeting. Her name's Cherry.

551
00:40:08,720 --> 00:40:11,080
That's why
you wanted to come to this festival?

552
00:40:12,840 --> 00:40:14,480
No wonder you were so eager.

553
00:40:14,560 --> 00:40:15,920
So do you see her?

554
00:40:16,480 --> 00:40:19,040
- I'll try texting her to ask where she is.
- Yeah.

555
00:40:20,520 --> 00:40:23,000
WHERE ARE YOU?

556
00:40:27,480 --> 00:40:29,960
I CAN SEE YOU NOW

557
00:40:31,520 --> 00:40:33,560
YOU CAN ONLY BRING ONE FRIEND

558
00:40:34,240 --> 00:40:36,840
I WANT THE ONE NEXT TO YOU

559
00:40:38,400 --> 00:40:39,480
We'll be right back.

560
00:40:39,560 --> 00:40:40,560
Let's go, Qin.

561
00:40:42,640 --> 00:40:44,400
No, not that one.

562
00:40:44,480 --> 00:40:46,000
NO, NOT THAT ONE

563
00:40:46,080 --> 00:40:47,000
Where you going?

564
00:40:48,000 --> 00:40:50,360
NO, NOT THAT ONE

565
00:40:59,760 --> 00:41:01,240
Who is he calling?

566
00:41:04,200 --> 00:41:05,680
You talk to him.

567
00:41:10,840 --> 00:41:13,120
Hi, Cherry.

568
00:41:13,680 --> 00:41:15,160
Where are you now?

569
00:41:17,000 --> 00:41:18,600
I can see you from here.

570
00:41:18,680 --> 00:41:21,440
But don't bring that friend with you.

571
00:41:24,800 --> 00:41:25,880
Yes.

572
00:41:25,960 --> 00:41:28,240
My friend likes that friend of yours.

573
00:41:28,320 --> 00:41:31,040
Okay, see you soon.

574
00:41:31,120 --> 00:41:32,880
Okay.

575
00:41:33,360 --> 00:41:34,240
All right.

576
00:41:36,360 --> 00:41:37,320
What now?

577
00:41:37,400 --> 00:41:38,480
We'll be back, Qin.

578
00:41:38,560 --> 00:41:39,640
- Hang out here.
- What?

579
00:41:39,720 --> 00:41:40,560
Come on, Kim.

580
00:41:41,120 --> 00:41:42,680
Where to? What about Qin?

581
00:41:42,760 --> 00:41:44,840
- What?
- Let's get some ginger tea.

582
00:41:44,920 --> 00:41:46,320
Cherry might be sick.

583
00:41:46,400 --> 00:41:48,640
Then she should've stayed home.

584
00:41:56,920 --> 00:41:58,680
Go now. Win Qin's heart.

585
00:41:59,120 --> 00:42:00,040
- Come on.
- What?

586
00:42:00,120 --> 00:42:01,480
Sending me alone?

587
00:42:01,560 --> 00:42:04,200
Dude, nobody confesses their love
in a group.

588
00:42:04,280 --> 00:42:06,040
- Are you nuts?
- Exactly.

589
00:42:06,120 --> 00:42:08,160
Stay here until you're ready then.

590
00:42:08,240 --> 00:42:09,880
We'll will buy you some time. Bye.

591
00:42:09,960 --> 00:42:11,240
Come on, Jamie.

592
00:42:19,360 --> 00:42:20,280
Qin.

593
00:42:37,240 --> 00:42:39,520
WHERE ARE YOU?

594
00:42:44,720 --> 00:42:46,120
Let's go back to Qin.

595
00:42:46,200 --> 00:42:47,440
Give me a sec.

596
00:42:47,920 --> 00:42:49,280
No, I'm done.

597
00:42:49,360 --> 00:42:51,320
She's ditching you for sure. Let's go.

598
00:42:51,880 --> 00:42:53,640
Keep them busy. I'll let Duang know.

599
00:42:53,720 --> 00:42:54,800
All right. Got it.

600
00:42:55,800 --> 00:42:58,040
WHERE ARE YOU?
I CAN'T FIND YOU

601
00:42:58,920 --> 00:43:01,280
Kim, I think she's coming.

602
00:43:01,360 --> 00:43:02,920
- Check this out.
- What?

603
00:43:06,320 --> 00:43:08,120
Qin, can I take a picture with you?

604
00:43:09,240 --> 00:43:10,680
Can I get a picture?

605
00:43:10,760 --> 00:43:11,920
Please excuse me.

606
00:43:12,000 --> 00:43:13,080
I'm in a hurry.

607
00:43:14,760 --> 00:43:15,760
Hey!

608
00:43:40,240 --> 00:43:41,720
I was calling him.

609
00:43:45,880 --> 00:43:48,040
- Not us.
- Not me.

610
00:43:49,880 --> 00:43:51,240
Well…

611
00:43:52,120 --> 00:43:53,440
I…

612
00:43:59,600 --> 00:44:00,760
My buddy likes you.

613
00:44:01,400 --> 00:44:02,320
Your buddy?

614
00:44:10,960 --> 00:44:12,120
My name is Buddy.

615
00:44:17,640 --> 00:44:20,080
I'm sick of it.
Another one like this.

616
00:44:20,160 --> 00:44:22,160
Hey, hold on. Calm down.

617
00:44:23,160 --> 00:44:24,200
I'm Duang.

618
00:44:24,280 --> 00:44:26,880
So is your name Buddy or Duang?

619
00:44:27,480 --> 00:44:28,480
It's Duang.

620
00:44:31,760 --> 00:44:32,960
Would you mind

621
00:44:34,240 --> 00:44:35,880
floating our krathongs together?

622
00:44:40,240 --> 00:44:41,840
Just say what you want.

623
00:44:43,040 --> 00:44:44,520
Can I try to win your heart?

624
00:44:46,120 --> 00:44:48,520
No, I'm going to win your heart.

625
00:44:48,600 --> 00:44:51,560
I'm not asking for permission.
I'm just letting you know.

626
00:44:55,880 --> 00:44:57,880
Then tell me, why me?

627
00:44:57,960 --> 00:44:59,240
- Your fair skin!
- What?

628
00:44:59,320 --> 00:45:00,880
Stop it. You'll ruin his chance.

629
00:45:02,720 --> 00:45:03,600
Amazing.

630
00:45:06,680 --> 00:45:09,040
I was trying to say
you have perfect skin.

631
00:45:09,600 --> 00:45:12,040
You've got beautiful eyes,

632
00:45:12,120 --> 00:45:13,720
a stunning nose,

633
00:45:14,280 --> 00:45:15,920
pretty lips,

634
00:45:16,480 --> 00:45:17,360
and even…

635
00:45:18,520 --> 00:45:20,160
perfect legs.

636
00:45:34,120 --> 00:45:37,040
I'm sorry. I didn't mean to say that.
The truth is I like you…

637
00:45:41,520 --> 00:45:43,360
because you sing beautifully.

638
00:45:51,000 --> 00:45:52,560
You're incredibly charming.

639
00:45:55,160 --> 00:45:58,240
I feel like I've been enchanted
all because of your voice.

640
00:46:41,480 --> 00:46:43,160
Good luck with that then.

641
00:47:06,880 --> 00:47:09,160
- Don't die.
- It's only the beginning.

642
00:47:09,920 --> 00:47:12,040
Yay!

643
00:47:12,120 --> 00:47:13,720
This is so embarrassing.

644
00:47:13,800 --> 00:47:14,840
- Hey!
- Hey!

645
00:47:43,280 --> 00:47:45,440
I've got it!
My plan is to make Qin mine.

646
00:47:45,520 --> 00:47:47,920
<i>There's a fine line</i>
<i>between pursuing and stalking.</i>

647
00:47:48,000 --> 00:47:49,720
<i>Why are you so in love with him?</i>

648
00:47:49,800 --> 00:47:51,800
Typically, a dog barks at a plane, right?

649
00:47:51,880 --> 00:47:54,280
But suddenly, the plane lets the dog in.

650
00:47:54,360 --> 00:47:56,560
<i>He's giving me a chance.</i>
<i>I gotta do my best.</i>

651
00:47:56,640 --> 00:47:58,520
<i>If he's uncomfy, then you're a stalker.</i>

652
00:47:58,600 --> 00:48:00,800
With how he's pursuing you,
are you uncomfy?

653
00:48:00,880 --> 00:48:02,960
<i>Do you know</i>
<i>you're causing people trouble?</i>

654
00:48:03,040 --> 00:48:04,200
<i>But I want to help.</i>

655
00:48:04,280 --> 00:48:05,560
<i>Then leave it to me.</i>

656
00:48:06,200 --> 00:48:08,080
<i>It's too early for me to give up.</i>

657
00:48:08,160 --> 00:48:09,280
<i>Prepare to be mine!</i>
